data.description: Welcome to your new home nestled in a serene and peaceful neighborhood! This charming single-family house offers comfort and convenience with its spacious layout and modern amenities. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warm and inviting ambiance of the open living spaces. The freshly renovated interior boasts three cozy bedrooms, providing ample space for relaxation and rest. The two well-appointed bathrooms feature contemporary fixtures and a touch of elegance. One of the highlights of this home is its brand new appliances, adding both style and functionality to the kitchen. Whether you're preparing a gourmet meal or simply enjoying your morning coffee, you'll appreciate the convenience and efficiency that these modern amenities offer. Outside, a large fenced-in yard awaits, perfect for entertaining guests, hosting family gatherings, or simply enjoying the outdoors in privacy. Let your imagination run wild as you envision gardening, playing with pets, or creating your own outdoor oasis in this expansive space. Located in a quiet and friendly neighborhood, this property offers the ideal blend of tranquility and convenience. With easy access to nearby amenities, schools, and parks, you'll enjoy the best of both worlds – a peaceful retreat and a vibrant community. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home. Schedule a viewing today and experience the comfort and charm that awaits
